msgid ""
"Definitions of Klein for Ray streaming, state, checkpoint, SQL, "
"scheduling, and operations terminology."
msgstr "Klein for Ray 流处理、状态、检查点、SQL、调度和运维术语的定义。"

msgid "Glossary"
msgstr "术语表"

msgid ""
"This glossary defines terms as Klein uses them. A similarly named Ray, "
"Flink, database, or broker concept can have a different lifecycle or "
"guarantee."
msgstr "本术语表按 Klein 中的含义定义术语。Ray、Flink、数据库或 broker 中名称相似的概念可能具有不同的生命周期或保证。"

msgid "Actor"
msgstr "Actor"

msgid ""
"A stateful Ray process addressed through a handle. Klein's native "
"streaming runtime uses actors for long-lived tasks and coordinators."
msgstr "通过句柄寻址的有状态 Ray 进程。Klein 的原生流处理运行时使用 actor 承载长时间运行的任务和协调器。"

msgid "Aligned checkpoint"
msgstr "对齐检查点"

msgid ""
"A checkpoint in which an operator waits for the same barrier epoch on "
"every active physical input before snapshotting state and forwarding the "
"barrier. Post-barrier input is held until the cut is complete."
msgstr "一种检查点：算子在快照状态并转发屏障前，等待每个活动物理输入上的同一屏障 epoch。屏障后的输入会被保留，直到一致性切面完成。"

msgid "At-least-once"
msgstr "至少一次"

msgid ""
"A delivery contract that preserves records inside its stated recovery "
"boundary but can repeat a logical record or external effect after "
"failure."
msgstr "一种交付契约：在其声明的恢复边界内保留记录，但在故障后可能重复某条逻辑记录或外部副作用。"

msgid "Backpressure"
msgstr "反压"

msgid ""
"Upstream slowing caused by bounded downstream capacity or a slow external"
" operation. In Klein it is visible through queue, transport, and "
"backpressure-duration metrics."
msgstr "由下游容量有界或缓慢的外部操作引起的上游减速。在 Klein 中，可以通过队列、传输和反压持续时间指标观察到它。"

msgid "Barrier"
msgstr "屏障"

msgid ""
"An ordered control message separating records before and after one "
"checkpoint epoch. A barrier cannot overtake earlier records on the same "
"edge."
msgstr "一种有序控制消息，用于分隔某个检查点 epoch 前后的记录。屏障无法越过同一条边上更早的记录。"

msgid "Batch execution"
msgstr "批处理执行"

msgid ""
"The execution path that lowers a compatible bounded Klein graph to Ray "
"Data Dataset operations."
msgstr "将兼容的有界 Klein 图下沉为 Ray Data Dataset 操作的执行路径。"

msgid "Bounded source"
msgstr "有界数据源"

msgid ""
"A source with a finite input that can eventually report completion. "
"Bounded describes input lifetime, not data size."
msgstr "输入有限且最终能够报告完成的数据源。有界描述的是输入生命周期，而不是数据大小。"

msgid "Changelog row"
msgstr "Changelog 行"

msgid ""
"A mapping carrying a `RowKind`: insert (`+I`), update-before (`-U`), "
"update-after (`+U`), or delete (`-D`). Dynamic-table queries and CDC "
"formats can emit changelog rows."
msgstr ""
"携带 `RowKind` 的映射：插入（`+I`）、更新前（`-U`）、更新后（`+U`）或删除（`-D`）。动态表查询和 CDC 格式可以发出 "
"changelog 行。"

msgid "Checkpoint"
msgstr "检查点"

msgid ""
"A coordinated, durable recovery point containing source positions, "
"managed state, timers, watermarks, and supported sink committables. A "
"completed checkpoint is published only after its referenced state is "
"durable."
msgstr "一种协调后的持久恢复点，包含数据源位置、托管状态、定时器、水位线和受支持的 Sink 可提交项。只有在其引用的状态持久化后，才会发布已完成的检查点。"

msgid "Checkpoint domain"
msgstr "检查点域"

msgid ""
"A weakly connected component of the physical streaming graph that shares "
"a checkpoint epoch. Disconnected components can make checkpoint progress "
"independently."
msgstr "物理流处理图中共享一个检查点 epoch 的弱连通分量。彼此断开的组件可以独立推进检查点。"

msgid "Checkpoint-transactional sink"
msgstr "检查点事务型 Sink"

msgid ""
"A sink that keeps prepared output private until the matching checkpoint "
"is durable and whose commit can be retried idempotently. This term "
"describes visibility at the sink boundary, not every side effect in an "
"end-to-end job."
msgstr ""
"一种 Sink：在对应检查点持久化前将已预备输出保持为私有，并且其提交可幂等重试。该术语描述的是 Sink "
"边界上的可见性，而不是端到端作业中的每个副作用。"

msgid "Chaining"
msgstr "算子链"

msgid ""
"Combining compatible adjacent operators into one physical task to remove "
"an actor and serialization boundary. The chain becomes one scheduling, "
"failure, and live-rescaling unit."
msgstr "将兼容的相邻算子合并到一个物理任务中，以消除一个 actor 和序列化边界。合并后的链成为单个调度、故障和在线扩缩单元。"

msgid "Collector"
msgstr "收集器"

msgid ""
"The runtime interface through which a source or operator emits records "
"and ordered control messages downstream."
msgstr "数据源或算子用来向下游发出记录和有序控制消息的运行时接口。"

msgid "Committable"
msgstr "可提交项"

msgid ""
"A serializable description of prepared sink output. The checkpoint "
"coordinator persists it and performs the second-phase commit after the "
"global checkpoint becomes durable."
msgstr "对已预备 Sink 输出的可序列化描述。检查点协调器会将其持久化，并在全局检查点持久化后执行第二阶段提交。"

msgid "Concurrency"
msgstr "并发度"

msgid ""
"The number of physical workers for an operator. In Ray Data, a `(min, "
"max)` tuple can describe an autoscaling actor pool; in native streaming, "
"the lower value is the initial parallelism and live changes are explicit."
msgstr ""
"一个算子的物理 worker 数量。在 Ray Data 中，`(min, max)` 元组可以描述自动扩缩 actor "
"池；在原生流处理中，下限值是初始并行度，在线变更需要显式执行。"

msgid "Control plane"
msgstr "控制平面"

msgid ""
"The components that compile, schedule, monitor, checkpoint, recover, and "
"control a job. They coordinate the data plane but do not proxy every "
"record."
msgstr "编译、调度、监控、检查点、恢复和控制作业的组件。它们协调数据平面，但不会代理每条记录。"

msgid "Data plane"
msgstr "数据平面"

msgid ""
"The ordered physical paths over which streaming tasks exchange records, "
"micro-batches, barriers, and watermarks."
msgstr "流处理任务交换记录、微批、屏障和水位线的有序物理路径。"

msgid "DataStream"
msgstr "DataStream"

msgid ""
"A lazy logical stream plus the operations required to produce it. Calling"
" a transformation builds a graph; a sink and terminal execution submit "
"it."
msgstr "一个惰性逻辑流及生成它所需的操作。调用转换会构建图；添加 Sink 并执行终止操作会提交该图。"

msgid "Detached actor"
msgstr "分离 actor"

msgid ""
"A Ray actor whose lifetime is not owned by the driver that created it. "
"Klein uses detached control actors so a submitted streaming job can "
"outlive its original driver."
msgstr ""
"生命周期不归创建它的 driver 所有的 Ray actor。Klein 使用分离的控制 actor，使已提交的流作业可以比其原始 driver"
" 存活更久。"

msgid "Driver"
msgstr "Driver"

msgid ""
"The Python process that builds the logical graph through module-level "
"APIs and submits it. The driver is distinct from the streaming "
"JobManager."
msgstr "通过模块级 API 构建逻辑图并提交它的 Python 进程。driver 与流处理 JobManager 不同。"

msgid "Dynamic table"
msgstr "动态表"

msgid ""
"The relational view of a changing stream. Each input change can update "
"the materialized table and produce one or more changelog rows."
msgstr "变化数据流的关系视图。每个输入变更都可能更新物化表，并生成一行或多行 changelog。"

msgid "Event time"
msgstr "事件时间"

msgid ""
"Time carried by records and advanced by watermarks, rather than the "
"worker's wall clock. Event time drives event-time windows and timers."
msgstr "由记录携带并通过水位线推进的时间，而不是 worker 的墙上时钟时间。事件时间驱动事件时间窗口和定时器。"

msgid "Execution mode"
msgstr "执行模式"

msgid ""
"`batch`, `streaming`, or `auto`. The selected mode applies to the whole "
"job."
msgstr "`batch`、`streaming` 或 `auto`。所选模式应用于整个作业。"

msgid "Execution graph"
msgstr "执行图"

msgid ""
"The physical graph after logical optimization, chaining, partitioning, "
"and expansion by concurrency. Its vertices represent deployable task "
"instances."
msgstr "经过逻辑优化、算子链合并、分区和按并发度展开后的物理图。其顶点表示可部署的任务实例。"

msgid "Idle input"
msgstr "空闲输入"

msgid ""
"A physical input temporarily excluded from a multi-input watermark "
"minimum because it has no data. It becomes active before a resumed record"
" is processed."
msgstr "因没有数据而暂时从多输入水位线最小值计算中排除的物理输入。恢复的记录被处理前，该输入会重新变为活动状态。"

msgid "Interactive mode"
msgstr "交互模式"

msgid ""
"A development mode in which a bounded terminal operation runs its graph "
"and returns a result immediately. It is separate from in-process debug "
"mode."
msgstr "一种开发模式：有界终止操作运行其图并立即返回结果。它与进程内调试模式不同。"

msgid "Job ID"
msgstr "作业 ID"

msgid ""
"The identifier used by the state API and published snapshots. In the "
"current streaming runtime it is the Klein Ray namespace; consumers should"
" still read the `job_id` field instead of deriving it."
msgstr ""
"状态 API 和已发布快照使用的标识符。在当前流处理运行时中，它是 Klein Ray 命名空间；使用方仍应读取 `job_id` "
"字段，而不是自行推导。"

msgid "JobManager"
msgstr "JobManager"

msgid ""
"The per-job control actor that owns job status, the execution graph, "
"scheduling, recovery, progress snapshots, and live operator rescaling."
msgstr "每个作业独有的控制 actor，负责作业状态、执行图、调度、恢复、进度快照和在线算子扩缩。"

msgid "Key group"
msgstr "键组"

msgid ""
"A stable bucket in the keyed-state hash space. Contiguous key-group "
"ranges move between subtasks when stateful operator parallelism changes."
msgstr "键控状态哈希空间中的稳定桶。有状态算子并行度变化时，连续的键组范围会在子任务之间移动。"

msgid "Keyed state"
msgstr "键控状态"

msgid ""
"Managed state scoped first to an operator and then to the current record "
"key. Klein exposes value, list, and map handles through "
"`KeyedStateContext`."
msgstr "先限定于算子、再限定于当前记录键的托管状态。Klein 通过 `KeyedStateContext` 提供值、列表和映射句柄。"

msgid "KleinContext"
msgstr "KleinContext"

msgid ""
"The advanced explicit owner used to isolate graph construction. Ordinary "
"module-level APIs keep this implementation detail out of application "
"code."
msgstr "用于隔离图构建的高级显式所有者。常规模块级 API 不会向应用代码暴露这一实现细节。"

msgid "Logical graph"
msgstr "逻辑图"

msgid ""
"The lazy user-facing graph before optimization, chaining, resource "
"planning, and physical task expansion."
msgstr "优化、算子链合并、资源规划和物理任务展开之前，面向用户的惰性图。"

msgid "Managed state"
msgstr "托管状态"

msgid ""
"State whose lifecycle, partitioning, snapshot, restore, TTL, and "
"rescaling are coordinated by Klein rather than manually stored in a UDF "
"object."
msgstr "生命周期、分区、快照、恢复、TTL 和扩缩由 Klein 协调的状态，而不是手动存储在 UDF 对象中的状态。"

msgid "Maximum parallelism"
msgstr "最大并行度"

msgid ""
"The fixed number of key groups configured by `state.keyed.max-"
"parallelism`. It bounds keyed operator parallelism and is checkpoint "
"compatibility metadata."
msgstr "由 `state.keyed.max-parallelism` 配置的固定键组数量。它限制键控算子的并行度，也是检查点兼容性元数据。"

msgid "Micro-batch"
msgstr "微批"

msgid ""
"A bounded group of logical records transferred together in the native "
"streaming data plane. It reduces RPC overhead without changing record-"
"level operator semantics."
msgstr "在原生流处理数据平面中一同传输的一组有界逻辑记录。它在不改变记录级算子语义的情况下减少 RPC 开销。"

msgid "Namespace"
msgstr "命名空间"

msgid ""
"The Ray namespace containing a streaming job's named actors. An explicit "
"`job.namespace` is useful for operations; otherwise Klein creates a "
"unique `klein-<job>-<id>` value."
msgstr ""
"包含流作业具名 actor 的 Ray 命名空间。显式 `job.namespace` 对运维很有用；否则 Klein 会创建唯一的 "
"`klein-<job>-<id>` 值。"

msgid "Object Store"
msgstr "Object Store"

msgid ""
"Ray's distributed shared-memory store for immutable objects. Klein can "
"cache large snapshot fragments there for fast recovery, but the Object "
"Store is not durable checkpoint storage."
msgstr "Ray 用于不可变对象的分布式共享内存存储。Klein 可以在其中缓存大型快照片段以加快恢复，但 Object Store 不是持久检查点存储。"

msgid "Operator"
msgstr "算子"

msgid ""
"A logical transformation or source/sink stage. Chaining can place several"
" logical functions in one physical operator."
msgstr "逻辑转换或数据源/Sink 阶段。算子链可以将多个逻辑函数放在一个物理算子中。"

msgid "Operator parallelism"
msgstr "算子并行度"

msgid ""
"The number of physical subtasks executing an operator. It is distinct "
"from Ray cluster node count and from `DataStream.rescale()` partition "
"routing."
msgstr "执行一个算子的物理子任务数量。它不同于 Ray 集群节点数量，也不同于 `DataStream.rescale()` 的分区路由。"

msgid "Partitioner"
msgstr "分区器"

msgid ""
"The routing policy from an upstream operator to downstream subtasks. "
"Built-in policies include forward, round-robin, rescale, broadcast, key, "
"and adaptive routing."
msgstr ""
"从上游算子到下游子任务的路由策略。内置策略包括 forward、round-robin、rescale、broadcast、key 和 "
"adaptive 路由。"

msgid "Processing time"
msgstr "处理时间"

msgid ""
"Time from the task process's clock. It can drive processing-time timers "
"but does not describe when an event occurred at the source."
msgstr "来自任务进程时钟的时间。它可以驱动处理时间定时器，但不表示事件在数据源处发生的时间。"

msgid "Replay buffer"
msgstr "重放缓冲区"

msgid ""
"Bounded upstream data retained until downstream progress acknowledges it."
" It supports single-task at-least-once recovery and fails fast at its "
"configured byte limit."
msgstr "在下游进度确认数据前保留的有界上游数据。它支持单任务至少一次恢复，并在达到配置的字节限制时快速失败。"

msgid "Resource plan"
msgstr "资源计划"

msgid ""
"The compiled description of operator concurrency, CPU/GPU requests, and "
"graph edges returned by `explain()` and optionally persisted for "
"inspection or override."
msgstr "由 `explain()` 返回的算子并发度、CPU/GPU 请求和图边的编译后描述，可选择将其持久化以供检查或覆盖。"

msgid "Restore path"
msgstr "恢复路径"

msgid ""
"The completed checkpoint URI supplied through `execution.savepoint.path` "
"when resubmitting a job. Despite the option name, Klein does not yet "
"create a separately managed Flink-style savepoint."
msgstr ""
"重新提交作业时通过 `execution.savepoint.path` 提供的已完成检查点 URI。尽管选项名称如此，Klein "
"尚不能创建单独管理的 Flink 风格 savepoint。"

msgid "Row kind"
msgstr "行类型"

msgid ""
"The change operation attached to a changelog row: insert, update-before, "
"update-after, or delete."
msgstr "附加到 changelog 行的变更操作：插入、更新前、更新后或删除。"

msgid "Sink"
msgstr "Sink"

msgid ""
"A terminal operator that publishes or collects a stream. Creating one "
"registers it for the next execution; passing sink roots to `execute()` "
"can select a subset explicitly. The older interactive terminal behavior "
"is deprecated."
msgstr "发布或收集数据流的终结算子。创建终结算子会将其注册到下一次执行；向 `execute()` 传入 sink 根节点可显式选择其中一部分。旧版交互式终结行为已弃用。"

msgid "Source"
msgstr "数据源"

msgid ""
"An operator that introduces records and source progress into a graph. A "
"source is bounded or unbounded and can participate in checkpoint "
"recovery."
msgstr "将记录和数据源进度引入图中的算子。数据源可以有界或无界，也可以参与检查点恢复。"

msgid "State backend"
msgstr "状态后端"

msgid ""
"The worker-local implementation of managed state. Klein currently "
"provides memory and optional RocksDB backends; both rely on durable "
"checkpoints for recovery across worker or cluster loss."
msgstr "托管状态在 worker 本地的实现。Klein 当前提供内存和可选 RocksDB 后端；两者都依赖持久检查点从 worker 或集群丢失中恢复。"

msgid "State TTL"
msgstr "状态 TTL"

msgid ""
"A policy that expires keyed state after an idle duration according to its"
" update and visibility rules. TTL bounds storage at the cost of "
"forgetting old relationships."
msgstr "一种策略：按照更新和可见性规则，在键控状态空闲一段时间后将其过期。TTL 以遗忘旧关系为代价限制存储。"

msgid "Streaming execution"
msgstr "流处理执行"

msgid ""
"Klein's native long-running actor runtime with ordered transport, managed"
" state, watermarks, checkpoints, replay, and recovery."
msgstr "Klein 的原生长时间运行 actor 运行时，具有有序传输、托管状态、水位线、检查点、重放和恢复能力。"

msgid "Subtask"
msgstr "子任务"

msgid ""
"One physical parallel instance of an operator, identified by a zero-based"
" subtask index."
msgstr "一个算子的单个物理并行实例，由从零开始的子任务索引标识。"

msgid "Timer"
msgstr "定时器"

msgid ""
"A keyed callback registered for a processing-time or event-time timestamp"
" and included in managed state snapshots."
msgstr "为处理时间或事件时间时间戳注册的键控回调，会包含在托管状态快照中。"

msgid "Two-phase commit"
msgstr "两阶段提交"

msgid ""
"A sink protocol that prepares output during processing and publishes it "
"only after checkpoint durability. Commit and abort operations must be "
"idempotent."
msgstr "一种 Sink 协议：在处理期间预备输出，仅在检查点持久化后发布。提交和中止操作必须幂等。"

msgid "Unbounded source"
msgstr "无界数据源"

msgid ""
"A source that can continue producing records indefinitely and therefore "
"selects native streaming execution in `auto` mode."
msgstr "可以无限期持续生成记录的数据源，因此在 `auto` 模式下会选择原生流处理执行。"

msgid "Watermark"
msgstr "水位线"

msgid ""
"An event-time progress statement. A multi-input operator uses the minimum"
" watermark of all active inputs, and an idle input does not hold back "
"that minimum."
msgstr "事件时间进度声明。多输入算子使用所有活动输入水位线的最小值；空闲输入不会阻碍该最小值推进。"

msgid "Window"
msgstr "窗口"

msgid ""
"A finite event-time grouping assigned per key. Klein supports tumbling, "
"sliding, and session window assigners through the native API."
msgstr "按键分配的有限事件时间分组。Klein 通过原生 API 支持滚动、滑动和会话窗口分配器。"
